00:12:15,970 --> 00:12:16,430
What...

299
00:12:18,980 --> 00:12:19,740
What if

300
00:12:20,520 --> 00:12:21,920
you lose control at night

301
00:12:22,030 --> 00:12:22,570
and hide yourself away

302
00:12:22,570 --> 00:12:23,700
in a deserted cave?

303
00:12:24,010 --> 00:12:25,030
