304
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:26,010
What should I do then?

305
00:12:26,010 --> 00:12:26,810
I can't leave.

306
00:12:26,970 --> 00:12:28,590
How could I be so fragile?

307
00:12:29,740 --> 00:12:30,670
Jiu'er is right.

308
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,080
You need

309
00:12:32,110 --> 00:12:33,180
a normal and calm person

310
00:12:33,180 --> 00:12:34,240
to take care of you.

311
00:12:35,100 --> 00:12:35,620
Otherwise,

312
00:12:35,620 --> 00:12:37,150
