316
00:12:55,680 --> 00:12:57,160
Why am I okay?

317
00:13:20,940 --> 00:13:21,660
Han Zheng.

318
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:22,340
W- What's wrong?

319
00:13:22,340 --> 00:13:23,740
Are you trembling again?

320
00:13:24,700 --> 00:13:25,210
No.

321
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:28,980
I just wanted to pull out my hand

322
00:13:29,530 --> 00:13:29,990
so that

323
00:13:30,300 --> 00:13:32,100
you can sleep more comfortably.

324
00:13:33,910 --> 00:13:34,730
Let me see.

325
00:13:34,900 --> 00:13:35,560
Other hand.

326
00:13:41,260 --> 00:13:42,460
You haven't trembled

327
00:13:44,820 --> 00:13:46,300
for four hours.

328
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:47,750
Isn't that good?

329
00:13:48,140 --> 00:13:48,840
You can finally

330
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,120
sleep in peace now.

331
00:13:55,630 --> 00:13:56,430
What's wrong?

332
00:14:00,890 --> 00:14:02,370
Tomorrow morning,

333
00:14:03,010 --> 00:14:04,470
if I find that fur has grown

334
00:14:04,700 --> 00:14:05,980
all over your face and body,

335
00:14:05,980 --> 00:14:07,010
and your condition has gotten worse,

336
00:14:07,010 --> 00:14:08,010
what should we do?

337
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:09,980
If that's the case,

338
00:14:10,690 --> 00:14:12,410
will you be scared of me?

339
00:14:12,860 --> 00:14:14,260
Will you stop liking me?

340
00:14:14,660 --> 00:14:15,700
I won't.

341
00:14:16,740 --> 00:14:17,660
I wish...

342
00:14:18,580 --> 00:14:19,780
I wish your whole body

343
00:14:19,900 --> 00:14:21,030
would be full of fur.

344
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:22,470
When that happens,

345
00:14:22,470 --> 00:14:24,670
no one will want to take you away from me.

346
00:14:25,460 --> 00:14:26,740
I'm just worried

347
00:14:27,260 --> 00:14:28,660
you won't be able

348
00:14:29,290 --> 00:14:30,000
to attend the Xuandong Grand Ceremony

349
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,100
because of that.

350
00:14:33,500 --> 00:14:34,230
In that case,

351
00:14:34,700 --> 00:14:36,010
I'll resign to fate.

352
00:14:36,740 --> 00:14:37,460
Besides,

353
00:14:37,880 --> 00:14:39,760
I am already prepared

354
00:14:40,090 --> 00:14:41,620
not to ascend to the throne.

355
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:46,010
Actually, I’ve been thinking.

356
00:14:46,530 --> 00:14:48,860
Isn't it a pity for you to give up the throne

357
00:14:49,290 --> 00:14:50,510
because of me?

358
00:14:51,980 --> 00:14:53,180
I have always thought

359
00:14:53,570 --> 00:14:55,310
you will be

360
00:14:55,340 --> 00:14:56,400
an even better king

361
00:14:56,580 --> 00:14:57,840
than the King of Xueqi.

362
00:14:59,540 --> 00:15:00,440
If I can still attend

363
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:01,780
the Xuandong Grand Ceremony,

364
00:15:01,780 --> 00:15:02,820
I will do my best.

365
00:15:04,230 --> 00:15:06,160
But if fate wants makes a fool of me,

366
00:15:06,260 --> 00:15:06,900
or

367
00:15:07,160 --> 00:15:07,820
