375
00:15:19,250 --> 00:15:20,340
How can you

376
00:15:20,370 --> 00:15:21,460
be so calm

377
00:15:22,180 --> 00:15:24,380
when faced with such a serious problem?

378
00:15:25,460 --> 00:15:26,520
Maybe it's because

379
00:15:27,820 --> 00:15:30,390
I have broken into the Qian palace,

380
00:15:31,050 --> 00:15:32,850
gone to jail, fallen into water,

381
00:15:33,100 --> 00:15:35,700
and had my Qi Vital Stone almost entirely dug out,

382
00:15:35,700 --> 00:15:36,300
but

383
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:37,100
I'm still

384
00:15:37,100 --> 00:15:37,960
alive and well.

385
00:15:38,500 --> 00:15:39,760
As long as I'm with you,

386
00:15:39,790 --> 00:15:41,650
I can get out of danger every time.

387
00:15:42,780 --> 00:15:44,110
It's the same this time.

388
00:15:44,860 --> 00:15:46,140
As long as we are together,

389
00:15:46,140 --> 00:15:47,600
we can solve this problem.

390
00:15:48,900 --> 00:15:49,960
Whether its ancestral return

391
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:50,760
or the throne,

392
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:52,820
we can deal with anything.

393
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:54,580
We just have to stay together.

394
00:15:56,530 --> 00:15:57,300
If we get through it

395
00:15:57,300 --> 00:15:58,130
this time,

396
00:15:58,600 --> 00:16:00,900
I want to bring you back to Shuobei immediately.

397
00:16:00,900 --> 00:16:02,630
At the Under the Moon Festival,

398
00:16:02,730 --> 00:16:04,330
in front everyone, I want to—

399
00:16:05,820 --> 00:16:06,310
What are you doing?

400
00:16:06,310 --> 00:16:07,110
Stop talking.

401
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:08,070
Why?

402
00:16:11,010 --> 00:16:12,340
Let me tell you a secret.

403
00:16:12,740 --> 00:16:14,140
I'm very afraid of people

404
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:16,500
making these kinds of promises to me.

405
00:16:17,100 --> 00:16:17,910
My father

406
00:16:17,940 --> 00:16:19,160
once promised me

407
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:21,220
he would come back

408
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:24,640
in time to bring me to the lantern festival.

409
00:16:24,940 --> 00:16:25,870
He did come back,

410
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:27,800
but

411
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:29,840
he had been poisoned.

412
00:16:35,820 --> 00:16:36,420
Poisoned?

413
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:38,170
I've got it!

414
00:16:38,740 --> 00:16:39,580
What is it?

415
00:16:40,190 --> 00:16:40,700
You guys are undergoing

416
00:16:40,700 --> 00:16:42,220
ancestral return for no reason.

417
00:16:42,220 --> 00:16:42,940
Could it be

418
00:16:43,130 --> 00:16:44,660
because you were poisoned?

419
00:16:46,700 --> 00:16:47,780
It's possible.

420
00:16:49,010 --> 00:16:49,860
How about this?

421
00:16:49,860 --> 00:16:50,720
Tomorrow morning,

422
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:51,950
I'll look through all the medical books

423
00:16:51,950 --> 00:16:53,020
in Jiuxiao City.

424
00:16:53,540 --> 00:16:54,420
I don't believe

425
00:16:54,710 --> 00:16:55,970
I won't find any clues.

426
00:17:06,380 --> 00:17:07,440
Ancestral return?

427
00:17:09,180 --> 00:17:11,109
This happened to Han Zheng as well?

428
00:17:11,260 --> 00:17:12,460
This is very strange.

429
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:14,579
If Han Zheng is unable to return to Shuobei

430
00:17:14,579 --> 00:17:15,510
because of this,

431
00:17:16,170 --> 00:17:18,970
it'll be no different from announcing to everyone

432
00:17:19,030 --> 00:17:21,740
that he's giving up his candidacy for the throne.

433
00:17:21,740 --> 00:17:23,540
The Xuandong Grand Ceremony...

434
00:17:24,940 --> 00:17:25,829
If Han Zheng is unable to

435
00:17:25,829 --> 00:17:27,700
make it back in time,

436
00:17:28,870 --> 00:17:30,550
who will benefit the most?

437
00:17:32,790 --> 00:17:34,120
King Mucha of Xuanqi.

438
00:17:34,700 --> 00:17:36,700
The Xuanqi is adept at making drugs.

439
00:17:36,930 --> 00:17:37,730
Could it be...

440
00:17:40,340 --> 00:17:41,460
If the Xuanqi tribe

441
00:17:42,510 --> 00:17:44,790
really did this

442
00:17:44,820 --> 00:17:47,420
to stop Han Zheng from ascending to the throne,

443
00:17:47,700 --> 00:17:48,700
and in the process

444
00:17:49,050 --> 00:17:50,050
even implicating

445
00:17:50,060 --> 00:17:51,920
our clanspeople in Jiuxiao City,

446
00:17:52,700 --> 00:17:53,840
then I don't have to

447
00:17:53,860 --> 00:17:54,780
tolerate

448
00:17:54,810 --> 00:17:56,340
their ambition any longer.

449
00:17:56,860 --> 00:17:58,990
What does the incident in Jiuxiao City

450
00:17:59,010 --> 00:18:00,020
have to do with me?

451
00:18:03,550 --> 00:18:06,350
Your Majesty’s ability to impute crimes to others

452
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:08,320
is really admirable.

453
00:18:13,780 --> 00:18:14,510
How dare you!

454
00:18:15,280 --> 00:18:16,180
King of Xuanqi,

455
00:18:16,480 --> 00:18:17,340
King of Cangqi.

456
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:19,760
Why did you bring troops into the palace?

457
00:18:19,980 --> 00:18:20,660
Why?

458
00:18:20,930 --> 00:18:22,860
I have a question for Your Majesty.

459
00:18:23,220 --> 00:18:24,150
How could you

460
00:18:24,180 --> 00:18:25,490
disregard

461
00:18:26,260 --> 00:18:27,950
the welfare of the Qi race

462
00:18:27,980 --> 00:18:28,820
in order

463
00:18:29,970 --> 00:18:31,300
to protect your throne?

464
00:18:31,740 --> 00:18:32,600
King of Xuanqi.

465
00:18:32,870 --> 00:18:33,620
Do you think nothing

466
00:18:33,620 --> 00:18:34,940
of rites and laws?

467
00:18:35,780 --> 00:18:37,960
That depends on

468
00:18:39,540 --> 00:18:40,270
whether our King

469
00:18:40,270 --> 00:18:41,550
thinks anything about

470
00:18:41,580 --> 00:18:43,240
the safety of the four tribes.

471
00:18:46,790 --> 00:18:47,650
King of Cangqi.

472
00:18:47,900 --> 00:18:50,430
You have always behaved in a measured manner.

473
00:18:50,820 --> 00:18:52,940
Why did you come here

474
00:18:53,780 --> 00:18:55,110
with the King of Xuanqi?

475
00:18:55,580 --> 00:18:56,380
Your Majesty.

476
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:58,030
Your son

477
00:18:58,060 --> 00:18:59,260
let my son, Keyuncha,

478
00:18:59,570 --> 00:19:01,370
die in front of him,

479
00:19:01,970 --> 00:19:03,370
and did nothing about it.

480
00:19:04,030 --> 00:19:05,330
Considering the bigger picture,

481
00:19:05,330 --> 00:19:06,130
I accepted it.

482
00:19:06,570 --> 00:19:07,290
But now,

483
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:09,940
the far north has been covered over by ice.

484
00:19:09,940 --> 00:19:12,300
Your Majesty didn't warn the people,

485
00:19:13,040 --> 00:19:14,430
and even blocked the flow of information

486
00:19:14,430 --> 00:19:15,660
to conceal it deliberately!

487
00:19:15,660 --> 00:19:16,990
I cannot stand for this!

488
00:19:18,260 --> 00:19:19,140
Everyone says

489
00:19:19,580 --> 00:19:21,220
the strange weather in recent years

490
00:19:21,220 --> 00:19:23,150
has to do with the loss of the Ember.

491
00:19:24,940 --> 00:19:26,880
I want the truth from Your Majesty.

492
00:19:28,290 --> 00:19:29,220
Is that true?

493
00:19:34,950 --> 00:19:37,080
If Your Majesty doesn't say anything,

494
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:38,030
that's fine too.

495
00:19:42,070 --> 00:19:42,700
Let’s go together

496
00:19:42,700 --> 00:19:44,100
to the Holy Fire Hall

497
00:19:45,380 --> 00:19:46,780
and we’ll know the truth.

498
00:19:55,010 --> 00:19:56,070
You don't have fur!

499
00:19:56,540 --> 00:19:58,470
Check if your hands are trembling.

500
00:19:59,500 --> 00:20:00,760
I don't think they are.

501
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:02,240
Great.

502
00:20:02,270 --> 00:20:04,330
Your condition hasn't gotten worse.

503
00:20:04,730 --> 00:20:05,650
Bad news!

504
00:20:06,970 --> 00:20:08,030
It's too serious!

505
00:20:08,140 --> 00:20:09,370
I'm so sleepy.

506
00:20:09,980 --> 00:20:11,420
I can't sleep.

507
00:20:11,570 --> 00:20:12,570
Young man,

508
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:13,860
you're so naughty.

509
00:20:17,020 --> 00:20:17,620
Poisoned?

510
00:20:18,160 --> 00:20:19,280
It's possible.

511
00:20:22,180 --> 00:20:24,340
I looked through all my mother's medical books,

512
00:20:24,340 --> 00:20:26,600
but I couldn't find these same symptoms.

513
00:20:26,780 --> 00:20:28,570
There are many kinds of poisons in the world.

514
00:20:28,570 --> 00:20:29,740
So I asked you all to come

515
00:20:29,740 --> 00:20:31,140
to brainstorm together.

516
00:20:33,250 --> 00:20:33,980
That's easy.

517
00:20:34,650 --> 00:20:35,050
Liu Fu.

518
00:20:35,710 --> 00:20:36,970
Send someone to collect all the

519
00:20:36,970 --> 00:20:38,620
medical books, medicinal books,

520
00:20:38,620 --> 00:20:40,400
and herbal manuals they can find.

521
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:42,330
Let's look through them one by one.

522
00:20:43,610 --> 00:20:44,830
Please bring the Qi language versions too.

523
00:20:44,830 --> 00:20:45,220
OK.

524
00:21:05,580 --> 00:21:06,640
I think I found one.

525
00:21:07,860 --> 00:21:08,290
Here.

526
00:21:10,190 --> 00:21:11,030
Can you understand it?

527
00:21:11,030 --> 00:21:11,630
I can't.

528
00:21:13,100 --> 00:21:14,110
Let me read it.

529
00:21:14,160 --> 00:21:14,760
I...

530
00:21:15,190 --> 00:21:15,790
Let me see.

531
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:17,350
This is Qi language, Mother.

532
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:17,990
General.

533
00:21:20,890 --> 00:21:22,620
Writings on Perculiar Plants.

534
00:21:23,950 --> 00:21:24,710
It records

535
00:21:25,030 --> 00:21:26,020
a kind of poisonous mushroom

536
00:21:26,020 --> 00:21:27,020
that grows

537
00:21:27,040 --> 00:21:28,370
in hot and humid places.

538
00:21:28,820 --> 00:21:30,470
After certain animals ingest them,

539
00:21:30,470 --> 00:21:31,870
they will spasm all over.

540
00:21:31,980 --> 00:21:33,240
They will also grow fur

541
00:21:33,420 --> 00:21:34,220
and fangs.

542
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:36,280
It's really very similar.

543
00:21:36,860 --> 00:21:37,390
Could...

544
00:21:37,620 --> 00:21:38,380
Could it be

545
00:21:39,060 --> 00:21:40,620
only a similar poison?

546
00:21:45,680 --> 00:21:46,340
Wait for me.

547
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:01,970
General.

548
00:22:03,980 --> 00:22:05,100
You are...

549
00:22:05,850 --> 00:22:07,020
According to the book,

550
00:22:07,020 --> 00:22:08,620
the calls of a cat can

551
00:22:08,650 --> 00:22:09,500
intensify its toxicity.

552
00:22:09,500 --> 00:22:10,500
Let's test it out.

553
00:22:11,020 --> 00:22:11,620
Stop it.

554
00:22:12,380 --> 00:22:12,840
Cat?

555
00:22:28,130 --> 00:22:28,730
Han Zheng.

556
00:22:28,960 --> 00:22:29,890
Are you alright?

557
00:22:36,520 --> 00:22:37,380
Your Highness!

558
00:22:40,190 --> 00:22:41,270
-Why is it so serious? -Keha!

559
00:22:41,270 --> 00:22:42,600
Save me, Your Highness!

560
00:22:53,170 --> 00:22:54,940
It seems this is the poison.

561
00:22:55,340 --> 00:22:56,340
It can't be wrong.

562
00:22:57,540 --> 00:22:58,860
The book also said

563
00:22:59,450 --> 00:23:00,270
this mushroom

564
00:23:00,340 --> 00:23:01,700
will only become poisonous

565
00:23:01,700 --> 00:23:03,020
when the surrounding temperature

566
00:23:03,020 --> 00:23:04,420
reaches a certain level.

567
00:23:04,790 --> 00:23:06,210
No wonder only Qi people were poisoned.

568
00:23:06,210 --> 00:23:07,340
Qian people haven't

569
00:23:07,420 --> 00:23:08,330
because Qian people's body temperature

570
00:23:08,330 --> 00:23:10,130
