571
00:23:10,540 --> 00:23:11,870
Who poisoned them then?

572
00:23:12,020 --> 00:23:13,860
Could it have been an accident?

573
00:23:14,780 --> 00:23:16,220
Such a rare poison

574
00:23:16,290 --> 00:23:17,950
