00:43:06,220 --> 00:43:06,880
So

1172
00:43:07,860 --> 00:43:09,130
I came to have a drink with you

1173
00:43:09,130 --> 00:43:09,970
and bid farewell.

1174
00:43:09,970 --> 00:43:12,230
Take it as an expression of my gratitude.

1175
00:43:13,740 --> 00:43:15,420
It's really the thought that counts

1176
00:43:15,420 --> 00:43:16,450
with you.

1177
00:43:17,810 --> 00:43:19,940
Don't you Qian have a saying that goes,

1178
00:43:20,070 --> 00:43:23,470
"Great benefactions do not need expressions of gratitude"?

1179
00:43:25,420 --> 00:43:26,310
Do you know why

1180
00:43:26,610 --> 00:43:27,870
I prepared wine today?

1181
00:43:28,840 --> 00:43:29,350
Why?

1182
00:43:30,220 --> 00:43:31,020
Because today

1183
00:43:31,570 --> 00:43:33,370
is my deceased wife's birthday.

1184
00:43:34,770 --> 00:43:35,970
The late Crown Princess and I

1185
00:43:35,970 --> 00:43:37,300
have the same birthday?

1186
00:43:38,170 --> 00:43:40,020
It's a kind of fate.

1187
00:43:41,910 --> 00:43:42,840
Happy birthday.

1188
00:43:51,970 --> 00:43:53,230
I'm suddenly curious.

1189
00:43:53,940 --> 00:43:54,920
What kind of person

1190
00:43:54,920 --> 00:43:55,720
was she?

1191
00:43:56,180 --> 00:43:57,840
What makes you so taken by her?

1192
00:44:02,590 --> 00:44:03,230
Suddenly,

1193
00:44:03,970 --> 00:44:05,770
I don't know how to describe her.

1194
00:44:06,580 --> 00:44:07,110
She was

1195
00:44:07,140 --> 00:44:08,420
a very rounded woman.

1196
00:44:09,250 --> 00:44:10,370
I've been talking about myself for a long time.

1197
00:44:10,370 --> 00:44:11,230
What about you?

1198
00:44:11,410 --> 00:44:12,540
What kind of husband

1199
00:44:12,620 --> 00:44:14,710
would a rational and decisive female general like you

1200
00:44:14,710 --> 00:44:15,750
choose?

1201
00:44:17,660 --> 00:44:19,090
I've never thought about it.

1202
00:44:19,090 --> 00:44:20,690
Do you have someone you like?

1203
00:44:24,370 --> 00:44:25,660
I didm

1204
00:44:26,860 --> 00:44:27,790
when I was young.

1205
00:44:28,780 --> 00:44:29,310
And then?

1206
00:44:29,970 --> 00:44:31,310
Did you confess?

1207
00:44:33,490 --> 00:44:34,770
Sadly,

1208
00:44:35,070 --> 00:44:35,990
I didn't get to

1209
00:44:36,500 --> 00:44:37,830
before he left Shuobei.

1210
00:44:39,210 --> 00:44:40,530
Sometimes I wonder

1211
00:44:41,250 --> 00:44:43,580
if things would have turned out different

1212
00:44:44,010 --> 00:44:44,640
had I

1213
00:44:45,200 --> 00:44:46,660
told him about it earlier.

1214
00:44:48,870 --> 00:44:51,130
There are many decisions to make in life.

1215
00:44:51,210 --> 00:44:53,540
That was the best one you made at that time.

1216
00:44:55,620 --> 00:44:57,820
But it doesn't mean you have no regrets.

1217
00:45:01,690 --> 00:45:03,470
If someone else asked me about this,

1218
00:45:03,470 --> 00:45:05,180
I would have kicked them into a lake.

1219
00:45:05,180 --> 00:45:06,290
I don't know why

1220
00:45:07,050 --> 00:45:08,380
I told you so much today.

1221
00:45:09,940 --> 00:45:11,000
Maybe it's because

1222
00:45:11,230 --> 00:45:12,230
we get along well.

1223
00:45:14,620 --> 00:45:15,220
By the way,

1224
00:45:33,980 --> 00:45:34,550
I know

1225
00:45:34,580 --> 00:45:35,710
a great sword maker.

1226
00:45:36,450 --> 00:45:38,180
I went to his place a few days ago

1227
00:45:38,420 --> 00:45:40,550
and found that he had made a new dagger.

1228
00:45:40,780 --> 00:45:42,180
It's sharp and lustrous.

1229
00:45:42,780 --> 00:45:44,020
I thought it's a good fit for you,

1230
00:45:44,020 --> 00:45:44,820
so I bought it.

1231
00:45:45,500 --> 00:45:46,160
Just in time

1232
00:45:46,550 --> 00:45:47,610
for your birthday.

1233
00:45:51,070 --> 00:45:51,670
Thank you.

1234
00:45:58,740 --> 00:45:59,980
I hope the Qian-Qi Six Treaties

1235
00:45:59,980 --> 00:46:01,260
will be signed successfully.

1236
00:46:01,260 --> 00:46:02,500
That way,

1237
00:46:02,520 --> 00:46:03,520
we can meet again.

1238
00:46:03,860 --> 00:46:04,700
When that time comes,

1239
00:46:04,700 --> 00:46:06,300
I will give you a gift in return.

1240
00:46:06,300 --> 00:46:06,760
We will.

1241
00:46:07,500 --> 00:46:08,560
We will meet again.

1242
00:46:11,090 --> 00:46:12,150
Stop the carriage.

1243
00:46:18,420 --> 00:46:19,350
The food is here.

1244
00:46:20,120 --> 00:46:21,120
Bring the food in.

1245
00:46:21,510 --> 00:46:22,380
Okay. Hurry.

1246
00:46:24,110 --> 00:46:24,580
Here.

1247
00:46:27,440 --> 00:46:28,130
Here, take it.
